move1.name: Psybeam
move1.description: The target is attacked with a peculiar ray. It may also confuse the target.

move2.name: Psychic
move2.description: The target is hit by a strong telekinetic force. It may also reduce the target's Special Defense stat.

move3.name: Shadow Ball
move3.description: The user hurls a shadowy blob at the target. It may also lower the target's Special Defense stat.

move4.name: Focus Blast
move4.description: The user heightens its mental focus and unleashes its power. This may also lower the target's Sp. Def stat.
